headline: BofA lists 13 SMID cap stocks that could rebound
summary: Investing.com -- Small and mid-cap (SMID) stocks are beginning to attract renewed interest after a long stretch of underperformance, according to Bank of America strategists, with signs of profit recovery and optimism around Federal Reserve cuts helping sentiment.
